supportDesc.extent: Part I: 182 folios (+ 1 unfoliated paper flyleaf at the end). Front flyleaf is foliated as folio 1. Part II: 6 folios;

layoutDesc.layout: Part I: 1- column(s); ruled lines: 21; written lines: 21; Initial words written in larger characters. Leaf catchwords on every verso. Part II: 1 column(s); ruled lines: 21; written lines: 32; Leaf catchwords on every verso.
